30
00:03:20,923 --> 00:03:22,925
DOBRO JE DA STE SVESNI, GOSPODINE.
ALI STVAR JE U TOME DA...

31
00:03:23,343 --> 00:03:24,344
MISLITE LI DA ÆE NAPAD NA
VILMINGTON BITI...

32
00:03:24,803 --> 00:03:27,806
